- **Domain**: waickoff.com (Wyckoff + AI)
- **Model**: Session-based pricing ($1/session)
- **Tech**: Claude Sonnet 4 API integration
- **Stack**: SMC + Wyckoff + Technical Indicators
- **Packages**: $5 (5 sessions) to $80 (200 sessions)
- **Payment**: PLACEHOLDER - Focus on features first

